Kittani Field Mechanic
The Kittani Field Mechanic is a technical specialist maintaining Kittani and
Splugorth technology in the field. They are highly valued by Splugorth forces
for their ability to repair alien equipment under combat conditions using
methods that most other races cannot replicate.

Kittani Field Mechanics choose from Technical, Electrical, and Physical skill
categories. Their knowledge of Kittani and Splugorth technology is unmatched
and they can often improvise repairs using alien materials unavailable to
other technicians.

Note: This OCC is restricted to Kittani race characters only.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12.
Starting equipment: Kittani field suit, advanced Kittani tool kit, computer
pad, one sidearm with energy clips.
